values: for you miss goldfishgeorge ;)

Does anyone want to join me in beating up the tooth-fairy?? does she really need to give him his teeth already. He's just four months old ....god dam-it and really ,does she have any sympathy for her fellow sisters nipples? Midnight tonight people- think of getting her back for all that pain she caused you when you were kids and she never paid enough ..in fact she put a price on your pain

Well finally on the 30th december after much pushing and amazing patience from my birth partners Garry and mum...thank you so much...Andrew arrived at 8.32 am. :) I can not and will not even to attempt to say what it's like ..we can only smile
I think Christmas in the form of little Tommy may be on his way!!!
Still around...does anyone have any suggestion of how to bring on labour....I've been in pre-labour on and off since friday..I have tried the spicy food and the sex thing...no luck
over it I just want to go to hospital. I'd put another photo up of my tummy...but i don't have a wide angle lens!!!
3 more shifts at oxford shop, selling suits ....yeah!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! bought cradle..... made monkey sheets!
so excited ...doing a photo shoot with Garth Knight on friday!!!

has anyone seen "the saddest music in the world"? by director Guy Maddin. Wow I think I have found my new faverouit dirctor... this man uses super 8 as a serious form to create a 20's and 30's look. It's worth seeing Isabella Rossellini with a pair of glass legs filled with beer!!! yep that's right prosthetic glass legs full of bubbling beer.  Must track down more of his movies
And still 8 weeks to go! starting to slow down now will have more time for live journal and stuff :)

tonight I turned up to work to find out one of the quietest girls that I occasionally have for ballet was the 16 year old killed in that Dural car accident last night. The car hit the telegraph with such force it snapped it..they had taken the car for a joy ride...where is the joy in that? How do you tell her class mates that Stephanie died last night...I had to tell one girl tonight that couldn't work out why everyone was so glum..stunned.

finally I'm back on line. It's been an interesting last couple of months from dealing with no more ninjitsu, no more aerial( yes that's stressing me out) say good bye to body and hello tummy and most of all hello hormonal RAGE!!! Yes that's me on enmore rd in the mornings giving serious abuse to anyone who gets in my way on the roads...had to stop myself wanting to get out and kicking  the shit out of people...oh the beauty of preparing for motherhood, it's amazing they there aren't a lot more pregnant woman in jail!!!!! But otherwise the best reminder of what it is all about is those gentle little kicks from within...feels really cool :) and sometimes it tickles. 
Despite buying pramms and baby clothes I still have a strong creative urge at the begining of july I took a group of students down to Melbourne for "Splash" the Australian choreographic competition and got  a great 2nd place in the professional division..yeah; that was something i wanted to do for years and was always afraid of doing i
I guess these two pictures says it all :)
finally no more internet places..now I can do this in the comfort of pJ's.......i like pj's :)
a student today asked an interesting question. Do blind people dream? and how if they have never seen before? is the imagination a lot wilder?     Any thoughts?
hi sorry I haven't been in contact with anyone but soooo HAPPY!!!!!!

Counting down ...so excited. In counting down I have also become very reflective..I don't know if I have grown up a lot the last year or I have a very different sence of reality, or I see things so much more clearly.  

In  the last week so many things that have been in limbo for last couple of months have resolved for the better, at last I am seeing a little bit of brightness and clarity.  It's been a year of waiting, a year of grief and sickness for quiet a few beautiful friends, I have gained a friend that I know is  dear to me and will be a life long friend no matter what. I have old friends who I have grown so much closer too. I gained a buisness partner and creative friend in two old freinds. I have been disappointed in another and no longer wish to give  it energy as I am so tired and there are many others I love that I want to support. And most importantly I have gained an amazing friend, lover and partner and know it isn't always going to be easy but I know it will be worth it :) 

I hope everyone has a brilliant year and Christmas 
love Marissa
crossing my fingers tonight I find out if Garry arrives on Christmas Day and yes I will be going to the airport with a big bow around me :) but i will have clothes on...(not for long)
Just like to say a big thankyou to Venus, Missy, bonedaddy , Kat and neotokyo for making Jingle Belles a great night thank you so much :)

Hi Guy's if anyone could help with posting this on Sydney Gothic forum it would be great...with a little tag about Missy , Minnie , Venus and Bonedaddy performing and Neotokyo and  Kat djing I would appreciate it ,as i am not on gothic forum. It's next to Katoomba station :)

As most of  you can see i am not very good at all with Lj not to mention myspace. No I don't know how to do load a vid and I am just struggling with pictures...I think this has a lot to do with not having a pc and spending most my time pointing my toes and throwing around big boys in hot studios, but soon I will have a pc and the net at home so if anyone will take pity on me and show me a few things during the holidays i would love it........And i promise no more blinding blue backgrounds!!!and maybe the guy at the internet cafe will not think i am interested in him because i spend so much time here
Finally I am starting to see some relief...in more ways than one  :) yes my  "candy pants" is coming to live in the land of Aus with me YEAH YEAH YEAH

This week already seems to be down hill. I recieved an e mail from a mother of a student of mine who is my biggest pride and joy and also like a little sister to me. She is in St vincints hospital in london with the worst and youngest case of anorexia they have ever seen at only 17 she is less than 35kg and is taller than me ,her heart is now malfunctioning. Besides this dad has thought it is a good idea that I take back the dog permanently from yesterday inh my one bedroom appartment when I only have 2 months to go before I get a house to live in with garry. And Garry well he seems to have gone missing can't contact him :(

Umm hear is a good one been asked to be the choeographic adviser for a song about Mr Troff man for Marti gras. Surprisingly the song is really good...so who knows what about this character I know a few things, but anyone with info would be great

Catherine I are putting together a new show for the Blue mountains friday the 14th of december line up should look a little like this..A number by Missy and minny (that is catherine and myself) a solo pole dance by Missy, a solo by minny( flamenco/ burlesque), a possible number by Herbie, A double new chair act with Venus and minny and much more to be confirmed...yeah including bloody good music and Dj's . bring your pjs and stay the night or what the hell just wear your pjs :)only silk or satin allowed!!
all is good :) like is happy..or getting better
No offence guys but closing down this sight just not into this stuff. Rather see people face to face.... take care my live journal and face book will be closed by friday night

Well finally one of my choreographies has been invited to be part of the Short And Sweet Dance performaCE as part of the wild card programe so if anyone want to see what I am really about none of this commercial crap that you normally see me do at clubs ..... it's on Sat the 20th  oct 2pm At the newtown theatre bookings through 1300 306 776 booking essential my work is short but one of the few choreographies that  was invited and not auditioned by request of the director :)

Sometimes when the bad news comes it's not so bad. I spoke to Danica this morning and she confirmed that the Sleaze Ball gig was cancelled due to a couple of reasons one being that other people not from the kirk troupe but other performers were being paid and we weren't. Two sides to the coin ....yes those other people are full on professionals such as the pole dancers but even supposedly the podium dancers were being paid and there wasn't even a budget offered to us for costumes. oh well I was still happy to get in there and train for a couple of days I still got a lot out it. Thanks Danica. :)
throw darts at little johnnys ass and get the bulls eye. Darts are in the shape of Bush. Actually the thought of johnnys ass is causing permanent dammage!!!how could I dress it ?

I got this gig but I don't feel ready yet. I think there will be a lot of bitching from other people  who are good at tissue. I chose to do  it despite everything because i think even though there are people out there that may be better than me I am not going to get anywhere unless i push myself. Is that fair?
what the hell before I finish spell check it's up...sorry guys

It's been a weird 24 hours. I managed to get a job that actually looks like it may fit into my teaching and Nimpo schedual... I'm very happy about. Danica asks if I can do Tissue at sleeze ball with her ...I am excited but shitting my pants, 8 metre high cieling . I had to laugh my job said they don't want me to start till october leaving free all of next week to reherse..yeah. Catherine calls from London asking  how to get to Camden (now she's sms from in Cyber Dog) oh yeah she got married in Verona...COOL. And garry called going in for more more surgery which may delay him moving here.. Not much happening at all !

This strange from not having anything at all to getting facebook, myspace and a livejournal in one week...be patient people roam was not built in a day but i will build something BIGGER and BETTER!!! thanks neotokyo
Strange from not having anything to getting myspace, facebook and a livejournal in a week. Patience people Rome was not built in a day but i'm planning bigger and better !!
